data.description: Wow! Welcome to this TURNKEY residence located within the centrally located Royal Saint Augustine Golf Course community, this charming residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and modern features, making it an ideal retreat for those seeking both style and functionality. The lot size is just under a third of an acer, allowing for plenty of space for pets and family gatherings to take place. The heart of the home lies in its updated kitchen, featuring new appliances, an oversized island, and updated fixtures. This culinary haven is not only visually appealing but also practical, offering a seamless space for creating meals and memories alike. Cozy up by the wood-burning fireplace in the living area, where high ceilings enhance the sense of space and airiness. The split floor plan ensures privacy, with a generously-sized master suite that boasts a huge closet for ample storage. Say goodbye to carpet maintenance, as the home boasts solid surface floors throughout. Custom wood trim on the walls adds a touch of character, creating an inviting atmosphere that resonates with both warmth and sophistication. Adding to the appeal are the practical updates: a 2021 HVAC system ensures year-round comfort, while a 2020 roof provides peace of mind for years to come. Whether you're a golf enthusiast or simply appreciate the tranquility of a well-kept community, this location offers a unique blend of natural beauty and convenience. Schedule your private tour today and discover how this property can seamlessly become your perfect home.
